&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Electric Hydrogen&lt;/strong&gt;’s mission is to make molecules to decarbonize our world! Our outstanding people are our most important asset and will allow us to deliver hydrogen from renewable electrolysis for heavy industry, at prices below fossil fuels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are seeking a CNC Machinist to support our manufacturing and engineering teams. In this role, you will collaborate with a diverse group of team members to manufacture precision components that advance our mission to decarbonize industrial processes through innovative hydrogen technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This position is based onsite in Devens, MA and reports to the CNC Supervisor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Interpret dimensioned part drawings to determine the appropriate machine tools, workholding, cutting tools, and inspection equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Set up, operate, and troubleshoot CNC lathes and mills, including making program offset edits and machine adjustments as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Perform complete machining operations from setup through production, including tooling setup, program proofing, part loading, and teardown&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Inspect in-process and finished parts using precision measuring equipment, including calipers, micrometers, height gauges, and hard gauges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Identify manufacturing bottlenecks and recurring production issues and recommend process improvements to increase shop efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Monitor machine performance and identify maintenance or safety concerns before they impact production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Maintain a clean, organized, and safe work environment while following established manufacturing procedures and quality standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with manufacturing and engineering teams to support continuous improvement initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;5+ years of experience as a CNC machinist with expertise operating both CNC lathes and mills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to independently set up, operate, troubleshoot, and optimize CNC milling machines for complex precision parts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Strong proficiency using precision measuring instruments, including calipers, micrometers, hard gauges, and height gauges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Ability to accurately read and interpret mechanical drawings and communicate drawing requirements to others when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Working knowledge of G-code and M-code with the ability to edit CNC programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Experience monitoring machining equipment and recognizing maintenance or safety issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Ability to lift up to 40 pounds, push heavy carts or crates, and perform physical activities including reaching, kneeling, stretching, and crawling as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Comfortable using computers for retrieving and recording production information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This role is available on either 1st or 2nd shift:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&q

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Electric Hydrogen&lt;/strong&gt;’s mission is to make molecules to decarbonize our world! Our outstanding people are our most important asset and will allow us to deliver hydrogen from renewable electrolysis for heavy industry, at prices below fossil fuels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are seeking a Corporate Development Analyst to support Electric Hydrogen on our path to rapid industrial-scale decarbonization. In this role, you will work within the Corporate Development team to support capital raising, strategic transactions, and long-term planning initiatives. You will be responsible for financial modeling, evaluating strategic opportunities, preparing presentation materials, and supporting due diligence activities across a range of transactions and operating procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;New York City candidates are preferred, with periodic travel to Boston and San Jose, reporting to the Head of Corporate Development. Fully remote arrangements may be considered for exceptional candidates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Analyze financial information and report on performance to internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Drive the accuracy of financial projections in partnership with cross-functional teams, including Strategic Finance, Sales, and Project Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Prepare detailed presentations, analyses, and memoranda for internal and external audiences related to capital raises, strategic transactions, and key business initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Support the evaluation of potential mergers and acquisitions, strategic partnerships, and investment opportunities across technology, manufacturing, operations, and project development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Assist with due diligence and transaction execution activities, coordinating internal and external stakeholders throughout the process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Support management and development of the EH2 investor model, including assumptions development, forecasting, and evaluation of new business opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Analyze industry trends, competitive dynamics, and market developments to inform strategic decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Support broader Finance and Corporate Development initiatives as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;1–3 years of full-time experience in investment banking, management consulting, corporate development, business operations, startups, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Finance, Engineering, Science, Business, Economics, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Advanced proficiency in Microsoft Excel and PowerPoint&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of financial statements, valuation methodologies, and financial analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills with the ability to derive insights from complex data sets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Ability to navigate ambiguity and perform effectively in a fast-paced, high-growth environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&q

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Electric Hydrogen&lt;/strong&gt;’s mission is to make molecules to decarbonize our world! Our outstanding people are our most important asset and will allow us to deliver hydrogen from renewable electrolysis for heavy industry, at prices below fossil fuels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;qMYqUG_convSearchResultHighlightRoot&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; data-turn-id-container=&quot;request-6a0b2f69-43bc-83ea-a19a-78d2ebfe64d4-5&quot; data-is-intersecting=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
