&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Electric Hydrogen&lt;/strong&gt;’s mission is to make molecules to decarbonize our world! Our outstanding people are our most important asset and will allow us to deliver hydrogen from renewable electrolysis for heavy industry, at prices below fossil fuels.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are seeking a Mechanical Engineer, Power Systems to join our growing engineering team. In this role, you will support the design and development of high-power electronic products used in hydrogen electrolysis systems. You will work cross-functionally with electrical, systems, thermal, and manufacturing teams to develop robust mechanical solutions from prototype through production.&lt;/p&gt;
