&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Partner with lead mechanical designers on the layout and integration of power systems, thermal management solutions, and structural designs from prototype through production release&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Create and release detailed drawings and documentation for parts and assemblies to support manufacturing and production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Perform detailed mechanical design of power bussing and bus interfaces for high-current DC output systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with systems optimization and modeling teams to evaluate power system performance and plant cost tradeoffs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Lead compliance efforts to certify products for US and EU markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Support manufacturing, testing, and field deployment activities as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Contribute to design for manufacturability, reliability, and serviceability across product development efforts&lt;/li&gt;
