&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of thermal management, structural analysis, and mechanical integration principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Experience with product development processes and electronics packaging&lt;/li&gt;
