&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Strong communication and cross-functional collaboration skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot;&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced, highly collaborative environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
