&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 2;&quot; data-start=&quot;1798&quot; data-end=&quot;2435&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Bachelor’s degree in Engineering or another technical field&lt;br&gt;• 8+ years of experience as a Project Manager&lt;br&gt;• Experience leading plant projects in petrochemical refining, renewable energy assets, gas processing, or power systems through the full project lifecycle&lt;br&gt;• Experience serving as the primary customer point of contact for major equipment or plant projects&lt;br&gt;• Understanding of EU project execution requirements and best practices&lt;br&gt;• Fluent in English&lt;br&gt;• Spanish fluency preferred&lt;br&gt;• Experience executing projects in Spain preferred&lt;br&gt;• Ability to travel up to 50% of the time during key project phases&lt;/p&gt;
